Untuk apa?

244
00:20:17,334 --> 00:20:18,418
Sia-sia!

245
00:20:20,045 --> 00:20:21,421
Tidak sia-sia.

246
00:20:39,731 --> 00:20:40,941
Tembak dia.

247
00:20:53,203 --> 00:20:55,539
Sial! Dari mana dia datang?

248
00:20:55,622 --> 00:20:57,415
Cepat pergi dari sini! Ayo!

249
00:20:58,959 --> 00:21:00,752
Kendali tidak berfungsi!

250
00:22:28,965 --> 00:22:30,049
Sial.

251
00:22:36,347 --> 00:22:37,807
Hentikan mobilnya!

252
00:23:14,552 --> 00:23:15,719
Di belakangmu!

253
00:23:19,181 --> 00:23:20,724
Dia menangkap roket?

254
