257
00:24:16,655 --> 00:24:17,906
Benar juga.

258
00:24:17,990 --> 00:24:19,866
Kau saja, kau tukang listrik.

259
00:24:27,332 --> 00:24:28,875
Tim Raptor, melapor.

260
00:24:28,959 --> 00:24:30,335
<i>Apa kondisimu?</i>

261
